Ann Codee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ann_Codee 0 Ann Codee (March 5, 1890–May 18, 1961) was a Belgian actress with numerous hit films on her résumé, such as Can-Can, Kiss Me Kate, and Interrupted Melody. Born in Antwerp, Belgium, her name was sometimes found in newspapers as Anna Cody.
